metadata.name: Butt Dad
metadata.description:
Butt Dad is a small clip that was uploaded to Reddit in 2017 and became a viral internet sensation shared by millions around the globe:

• Made it to #1 on the front page of Reddit

• As seen in the U.S. and Canada on multiple national television commercials

• Featured on MTV's "Ridiculousness"

This small clip lives in every smart phone's GIF picker under "Funny" or "Parenting" and makes the rounds annually on Father's Day.

I am the original owner of this iconic clip and am minting the original, trimmed, high-resolution video file.
